Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of RPost, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
RPost, Inc. provides email delivery proof, encryption, and e-signatures technology services for companies worldwide. The company offers RMail Services, a registered email services platform to provide proof of email delivery, content, and official time; LegalProof records for proving legality of email; Registered Receipt return email, an on-demand reconstruction of original message content; and Digital Seal time stamp and message authentication services. It also provides eSignOff service enabling the message recipients to electronically sign and timestamp emails and attachments; eContract service that allows to electronically sign and timestamp an email message and attachment by creating a en...
RPost, Inc. provides email delivery proof, encryption, and e-signatures technology services for companies worldwide. The company offers RMail Services, a registered email services platform to provide proof of email delivery, content, and official time; LegalProof records for proving legality of email; Registered Receipt return email, an on-demand reconstruction of original message content; and Digital Seal time stamp and message authentication services. It also provides eSignOff service enabling the message recipients to electronically sign and timestamp emails and attachments; eContract service that allows to electronically sign and timestamp an email message and attachment by creating a enforceable contract; Proof Archive Service, a management tool to archive a copy of the evidentiary record of the email transaction in a master repository; SecuRmail, an encryption email service; Register Reply that records a back-and-forth discussion or negotiation with an internal or external party; and SideNote, which lets the sender to add context for CC and BCC recipients in the form of private comments and instructions on the original message. In addition, the company offers RPost Cloud platform that processes legal electronic messaging; LargeMail service enabling to attach up to 200MB of files per email message; R-PDF form, a smart technology that captures client's mouse-scripted legal electronic signature or indication of acceptance of terms; and Certified Email Service, an email service that provides the recipient of the Certified Email message with a means to authenticate the message origin, author, and content. The company serves legal, governments, insurance agents and brokers, insurance carriers, real estate, travel, factoring/ABL, auditing, telecom carriers, financial services, franchise, engineering, and pharmaceutical companies. The company was founded in 2000 and is based in Los Angeles, California. RPost, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Rpost Communications Ltd.
