RPost, Inc. Key Developments

RPost's Update for RMail Brings Enhanced Cybersecurity and Collaboration Features
Oct 25 16
RPost announced an extensive update has arrived to RPost's cyber-security product RMail, the all-in-one service that empowers email users' Microsoft Outlook and Gmail interfaces  with sending options including email encryption, open tracking, certified delivery proof, e-signatures, and secure large file transfers.  RMail® has been relied upon for important messaging by governments and businesses of all sizes for more than a decade. Three new technologies inside the latest RMail product include Anti-Whaling™ Imposter Protection, an 'Automatic' email encryption mode, and Secure File Share large file transfer. RMail's Anti-Whaling Imposter Protection feature protects Microsoft Outlook users against "whaling" attacks, also known as "Business Email Compromise" (BEC) attacks. RPost has also made important changes to the email encryption functionality within RMail, allowing for improved ease-of-use without sacrificing security. When sending an encrypted email message with RMail, there is a new 'Automatic' mode for secure sending that automatically detects and selects the easiest secure sending method available considering the recipient user experience, for each recipient destination. In all situations, RMail uses its patented True Direct Delivery™ encryption technology so that the recipient does not need to register for an account or go to a 3rd party website to retrieve the message content, and there is no message storage in the middle or on the web.


RPost Partners with Broker Network to Offer RMail
Sep 13 16
RPost announced a new partnership with Broker Network to further assist more than 600 UK insurance brokers with secure email, e-signatures and auditable proof of email delivery, all designed to assist Brokers in complying with the new Act. RPost's RMail service integrates seamlessly with Microsoft Outlook, Office 365 and Gmail, and can also be used via an iPad App or with backoffice, web or CRM integration options. RPost technology has been endorsed for compliance and cyber security by Broker Networkand BIBA.


RPost, Inc. Presents at Investment Trends Summit, Sep-29-2015 08:10 AM
Sep 25 15
RPost, Inc. Presents at Investment Trends Summit, Sep-29-2015 08:10 AM. Venue: Four Seasons Resort The Biltmore Santa Barbara, 1260 Channel Drive, Santa Barbara, CA 93108, United States.


