Dr. Terrance Tomkow
Chief Technology Innovation Officer
VIEW BIO





Dr. Terrance Tomkow
Chief Technology Innovation Officer
VIEW BIO




Dr. Terrance Tomkow
Chief Technology Innovation Officer
Tomkow drives technology vision and innovation at RPost. He is one of the pioneers of electronic mail with more than 20 years of email software innovation. He authored one of the first electronic mail packages, which won PC Magazine’s Editor’s Choice award, and was a University Lecturer on Logic and Artificial Intelligence. Tomkow has developed 19 email software patents and holds a Doctor of Philosophy degree from Cambridge University in the United Kingdom.

