Luis Zambrano
Vice President of Finance & Operations
Zambrano oversees general business operations and finance for RPost. He has several years of strategic planning, marketing, product development and process reengineering experience with Telefónica, a major telecommunications company in Europe and Latin America, and Citibank. A native of Argentina, Zambrano holds a Bachelor of Science degree in Industrial Engineering from the Buenos Aires Institute of Technology and an MBA from the UCLA Anderson School of Management.

