Fernando Neves
Business Director, Brazil
Neves, with more than 25 years of business management experience in multi-national companies, heads RPost’s Brazil operations. Neves has built and run several technology companies, acting as CEO, country manager and vice president of business development. He has also consulted for large enterprise companies in the US, Europe and Latin America, and has served for several years as a member of the Lotus/IBM Business Partner Executive Council. Neves, a native of Brazil, holds a Bachelor’s degree in Information Technology from São Paulo State Technological College (FATEC) in Brazil and is a graduate of several executive programs at the MIT-Sloan School of Business.

