Platforms
Our platforms enable organizations of all sizes
to transact business faster, easier, and more securely
than ever before.







 
RMail: Empower Your Email
RMail is an all-in-one solution for powerful email, with simple-to-use open tracking, delivery proof, email encryption, electronic signatures, large file transfer functionality and more. Powered by Registered Email™ technology, RMail provides a Registered Receipt™ record for every message sent, providing and proving important details of the correspondence. RMail works seamlessly with users’ existing email platforms, including Microsoft Outlook, Gmail, and others.
 Go to RMail.com						
learn more





 
RSign:  E-Sign Made Simple
RSign is a web-based app that makes it easy to prepare and send any document to be signed electronically by anyone, anywhere, and on almost any device.
 Go to RSign.com						
learn more





 
RForms: Create and Automate Fillable PDF Forms
A full-service solution for enterprise form automation, RForms enables any form to be filled, saved, and submitted electronically using any PDF reader. RForms solution consultants are available to assist customers every step of the way, from initial form preparation to configuring an optional data extract into an XML file and more.
 Learn more						
learn more





 
RPostal: Extend Your Postal Reach into the World of Email
RPostal enables postal operators to expand their reach into the world of email. Powered by Registered Email™ technology, RPostal makes it easy for postal operators to offer commercial e-postal services such as Registered Email™ messages and secure electronic document delivery, resulting in increased customer satisfaction and revenues.
 Learn more						
learn more




















